title: Joey Diaz - Back to Colorado
itunes:title: Joey Diaz - Back to Colorado
description:
My HoneyDew this week is Joey Diaz! The saga continues as we cover 1985-1986. Joey leaves New Jersey and heads back to Colorado. If you’re all in on Joey’s life story, it’s a wild ride. This episode is no exception. I love Joey Diaz but he’s the reason I lock my doors, even if I’m just going to get the mail.

SUBSCRIBE to my YouTube channel & watch The Dew there every toozdee! https://www.youtube.com/rsickler
